  "title": "Rich Buttery Egyptian Provola Tagine",
  "description": "A buttery and molten Egyptian dish featuring provola cheese, namul, and spices, cooked to perfection in a wok. This dish is a twist on traditional Egyptian cuisine with a rich and creamy sauce.",
