  "instructions": [
    "Heat the butter and olive oil in a wok over medium heat.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook until fragrant.",
    "Add the namul and cook until it starts to brown.",
    "Add the provola cheese and stir until it starts to melt.",
    "Add the cumin and paprika and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir the mixture occasionally to prevent burning.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
